subtasks.details:
• In backend/db/migrations/0001_add_indexes.sql write:
  CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_flights_flight_no ON flights(flight_no);
  CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_flights_gate ON flights(gate);
  CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_personnel_employee_id ON personnel(employee_id);
• Execute the script during container start-up (ENTRYPOINT sh that runs `sqlite3 $DB_PATH < migrations/0001_add_indexes.sql`).
• Verify existence with `PRAGMA index_list('flights')` etc.
• Benchmark with `EXPLAIN QUERY PLAN` and Python perf test; assert average <10 ms over 1 000 randomized queries.

